<item>
            <title>[LU-253] 1.8 and 2.1 Patched kernels are indistinguishable to a user.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-253</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;After installing a patched kernel from build.whamcloud.com, it is not possible to reliably distinguish if this kernel is patched for 1.8 Lustre or 2.1 Lustre.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="10672">LU-253</key>
            <summary>1.8 and 2.1 Patched kernels are indistinguishable to a user.</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=11303&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
